(is an element of,is an element of boolean OR q) -fuzzy bi-ideals
paper_abstract: In this paper, using the idea of quasi-coincidence of a fuzzy point with a fuzzy set, the concepts of (is an element of, is an element of boolean OR q) - fuzzy subsemigroup and (is an element of, is an element of boolean OR q) - fuzzy bi-ideal in a Gamma -semigroup have been introduced and some related properties have been investigated.
